---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Investor Hub — Strategic Transformations"
  description="Strategic Transformations is scaling its structural burnout methodology into a multi-product, multi-channel enterprise. Review the investment thesis, traction, and opportunity."
  section="st"
  accentColor="teal"
>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-st-gradient"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-teal-DEFAULT"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 70% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-mid relative z-10">
      <img src="/logos/st-logo.svg" alt="Strategic Transformations" width="220" height="44" class="h-9 w-auto mb-6 animate-on-scroll" />
      <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex animate-on-scroll">Investor Hub · Confidential Overview</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl text-light font-bold mb-5 animate-on-scroll">
        The $88B Burnout<br/>
        <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT">Market Has No</span><br/>
        Structural Answer.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-xl mb-3 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.1s">Until now.</p>
      <p class="text-muted text-base max-w-2xl mb-10 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.15s">
        Strategic Transformations is a structural burnout consultancy with a proprietary diagnostic framework,
        a growing multi-channel product ecosystem, a published author platform, and a founder whose
        lived authority cannot be manufactured or replicated. We are building toward scale —
        and seeking aligned capital partners to accelerate the work.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
        <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-teal">Request Investor Briefing →</a>
        <a href="/structural-burnout/services" class="btn-outline-teal">View Service Architecture</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-6 animate-on-scroll italic">
        Market figures are sourced from publicly available industry research. Projections are
        forward-looking strategic modeling, not guarantees. Full investor deck available upon request after briefing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── KEY METRICS STRIP ─────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-y border-border py-8">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        {[
          { num: '$88B+',  label: 'Global Burnout Economic Cost', source: 'Gallup / WHO estimates' },
          { num: '77%',    label: 'Workers Reporting Burnout',    source: 'Gallup State of Global Workplace' },
          { num: '2–3×',  label: 'Salary Cost to Replace Burned-Out Employee', source: 'SHRM / industry research' },
          { num: '$1.1T', label: 'US Productivity Loss from Disengagement', source: 'Gallup 2024 estimate' },
        ].map((m) => (
          <div>
            <p class="font-heading text-3xl text-teal-DEFAULT font-bold">{m.num}</p>
            <p class="text-light text-xs font-semibold mt-2 leading-snug">{m.label}</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-1 italic">{m.source}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── THE MARKET PROBLEM ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Market Problem</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">
          A multi-billion dollar problem.<br/>
          <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT">Zero structural solutions.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          The burnout market has generated massive investment — and virtually none of it
          addresses the actual source of the problem.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-10">
        {[
          {
            label: 'The Wellness Industry',
            size: '$61B+ market',
            problem: 'Treats burnout as an individual wellness failure. Mindfulness apps, EAPs, resilience trainings. All downstream.',
            failure: 'None of it changes the structure producing the exhaustion. Market keeps growing because the interventions don\'t work.',
          },
          {
            label: 'Traditional HR Consulting',
            size: '$37B+ market',
            problem: 'Engagement surveys, pulse checks, policy recommendations. Measures symptoms without structural diagnosis.',
            failure: 'Output is a report. Not recalibration. Organizations pay for data they already have without a path to change.',
          },
          {
            label: 'DEI & Culture Programs',
            size: '$9.3B market',
            problem: 'Valuable but typically siloed. Addresses belonging without diagnosing the structural strain marginalizing people.',
            failure: 'People feel seen. Still burned out. The architecture of harm remains intact.',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="card border-red-500/15 animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3 gap-3">
              <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">{item.label}</p>
              <span class="text-xs text-muted border border-border rounded px-2 py-0.5 shrink-0">{item.size}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">{item.problem}</p>
            <div class="border-t border-red-500/15 pt-3">
              <p class="text-red-400/80 text-xs flex items-start gap-1.5">
                <span class="shrink-0">✗</span>{item.failure}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/40 bg-teal-glow p-8">
          <p class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
            Strategic Transformations fixes the design.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            The only practitioner-developed framework that treats burnout as what it is — a structural failure —
            and delivers a diagnostic and recalibration pathway that addresses it at the root. Not downstream.
            Not symptomatic. Structural.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── THE SOLUTION & PRODUCT ECOSYSTEM ─────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">The Solution</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">
          A proprietary framework with<br/>multi-channel revenue architecture.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">

        <!-- Left: Framework -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold mb-4">The UNMASK Framework</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The UNMASK Framework is not a product — it is a diagnostic operating system.
            Developed through direct organizational consulting practice, it surfaces and addresses
            the six structural conditions most responsible for organizational burnout, attrition,
            and silenced capacity. It is deployable across services, licensed products, institutional
            training, and emerging AI-enhanced tools.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            {[
              { letter: 'U', name: 'Uncover', desc: 'Hidden strain patterns' },
              { letter: 'N', name: 'Name',    desc: 'Architectural conditions' },
              { letter: 'M', name: 'Map',     desc: 'Organizational impact zones' },
              { letter: 'A', name: 'Align',   desc: 'Structural redesign pathways' },
              { letter: 'S', name: 'Sustain', desc: 'Recalibration into operations' },
              { letter: 'K', name: 'Keep Watch', desc: 'Accountability infrastructure' },
            ].map((p) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 py-2 border-b border-border/60">
                <span class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT text-lg font-bold w-6 shrink-0">{p.letter}</span>
                <span class="text-light text-sm font-semibold w-28 shrink-0">{p.name}</span>
                <span class="text-muted text-sm">{p.desc}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-teal-DEFAULT/25 rounded-md p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-2">Competitive Moat</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
              The founder's practitioner authority, Army veteran discipline, womanist theological grounding,
              and graduate-level academic credibility create a combination of lived and intellectual authority
              that institutional wellness vendors and traditional HR consultants cannot replicate.
              The methodology is proprietary. The credibility is non-transferable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Revenue channels -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold mb-4">Revenue Architecture</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            {[
              {
                channel: 'High-Ticket Consulting Services',
                range: '$22,000 – $45,000+',
                desc: 'UNMASK Diagnostic, Recalibration Engagement, AI Audit, Retainer. High-margin, high-touch.',
                status: 'Active',
              },
              {
                channel: 'Speaking & Keynotes',
                range: '$12,500 – $15,000+',
                desc: '5 signature talks. Conference circuit, corporate events, academic institutions. Recurring revenue pipeline.',
                status: 'Active',
              },
              {
                channel: 'UNMASK Blueprint Series',
                range: 'Individual + Institutional Licensing',
                desc: 'Three published volumes. Digital and physical. Institutional licensing at scale. Growing product revenue stream.',
                status: 'Active',
              },
              {
                channel: 'URI Formation',
                range: '$5,000 – $15,000+',
                desc: 'Justice-centered leadership formation. Faith-based, nonprofit, and academic markets. Mission-aligned revenue.',
                status: 'Active',
              },
              {
                channel: 'UNMASK SaaS / Digital Platform',
                range: 'Subscription TBD',
                desc: 'Interactive UNMASK diagnostic platform — in development. Scalable, recurring revenue layer with institutional licensing potential.',
                status: 'In Development',
              },
              {
                channel: 'Enterprise Framework Licensing',
                range: 'Scope-Based',
                desc: 'UNMASK licensed for organizational-wide deployment, practitioner certification programs, and white-label consulting infrastructure.',
                status: 'Pipeline',
              },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-md hover:border-teal-DEFAULT/40 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap mb-1">
                    <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-sm">{item.channel}</p>
                    <span class={`text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded border font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-wide ${
                      item.status === 'Active' ? 'text-teal-DEFAULT border-teal-DEFAULT/40 bg-teal-DEFAULT/10' :
                      item.status === 'In Development' ? 'text-gold border-gold/40 bg-gold/10' :
                      'text-muted border-border'
                    }`}>{item.status}</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs font-semibold mb-1">{item.range}</p>
                  <p class="text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── FOUNDER PROFILE ───────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Founder</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-light">
          Authority that cannot be manufactured.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-3 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          The founder is not a consultant who found a niche. She is a practitioner
          who built a diagnostic system from the inside of the problem.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            icon: '🎖️',
            label: 'Army Veteran',
            desc: 'Military discipline, crisis leadership, and organizational systems thinking applied to a civilian burnout epidemic. Leadership under real pressure — not theoretical.',
          },
          {
            icon: '✍🏾',
            label: 'Practitioner-Scholar',
            desc: 'Graduate work in Religions, Ethics & Public Intellectuals. Womanist theology as epistemological foundation — not decoration. Academic rigor meeting field-tested practice.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🏗️',
            label: 'Framework Creator',
            desc: 'UNMASK developed through direct organizational consulting — not academic theory. The IP is proprietary. The methodology is tested across sectors.',
          },
          {
            icon: '📖',
            label: 'Published Author',
            desc: 'Three-volume UNMASK Blueprint Series positions ST as thought leadership, not just services. The books create inbound pipeline at scale.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🌐',
            label: 'Liberation Grounded',
            desc: 'Womanist ethics and liberation philosophy provide a justice-centered intellectual framework that differentiates ST in a market of performance-optimization consultants.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🤝',
            label: 'Cross-Sector Track Record',
            desc: 'Nonprofit, faith-based, corporate, government, higher education. Structural burnout is not industry-specific. Neither is the solution.',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
            <span class="text-2xl block mb-3">{item.icon}</span>
            <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-sm mb-2">{item.label}</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── TRACTION SIGNALS ──────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.05) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Traction</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-light">What's already in motion.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-3 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          Strategic Transformations is generating revenue and building the platform for scale.
          Seed capital is not for survival — it is for acceleration.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {[
          {
            area: 'Published Intellectual Property',
            items: [
              'UNMASK Blueprint Series — 3 volumes published',
              'UNMASK Interactive Web Application live',
              'Proprietary diagnostic framework fully documented',
              'IP protection and licensing infrastructure in development',
            ],
          },
          {
            area: 'Active Service Delivery',
            items: [
              'Consulting engagements across nonprofit, corporate, and faith-based sectors',
              'Speaking and keynote pipeline active',
              'Executive coaching and organizational advisory work',
              'URI Formation engagements in execution',
            ],
          },
          {
            area: 'Platform & Systems',
            items: [
              'GoHighLevel CRM with lead capture and pipeline automation',
              'UNMASK digital checkout infrastructure live (unmask.nikkicates.com)',
              'Consolidated digital ecosystem (nikkicates.github.io) in deployment',
              'Newsletter infrastructure active via The Unbothered Collective',
            ],
          },
          {
            area: 'Network & Authority Building',
            items: [
              'BNI membership active — professional referral network engaged',
              'Graduate academic work in progress — credentialing the methodology',
              'Conference speaking circuit development',
              'ATHENA NextGen leadership program pipeline (Orlando)',
            ],
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
            <p class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold mb-4">{item.area}</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {item.items.map((i) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-muted">
                  <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0">→</span>{i}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── SEED CAPITAL USE ──────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Seed Capital</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-light">What capital unlocks.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-3 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          The foundation is built. The IP is documented. The market is proven.
          Capital accelerates the three things that compound fastest: product, platform, and pipeline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-10">
        {[
          {
            area: 'Product Development',
            icon: '🛠️',
            items: [
              'UNMASK SaaS platform — full buildout and institutional-grade deployment',
              'AI-enhanced diagnostic tools integrated into the UNMASK engine',
              'Enterprise licensing and practitioner certification infrastructure',
              'Vol. 4 and advanced content development',
            ],
          },
          {
            area: 'Market Expansion',
            icon: '📡',
            items: [
              'National speaking circuit acceleration — 10+ conferences annually',
              'Corporate and enterprise client pipeline scaling',
              'Academic and higher education partnerships',
              'International expansion — starting with Caribbean and African diaspora markets',
            ],
          },
          {
            area: 'Operational Infrastructure',
            icon: '⚙️',
            items: [
              'Team expansion: operations, client success, content',
              'Full IP protection, trademark, and legal infrastructure',
              'Marketing and thought leadership amplification',
              'CRM and fulfillment systems optimization at scale',
            ],
          },
        ].map((bucket) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
            <span class="text-2xl block mb-3">{bucket.icon}</span>
            <p class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold mb-4">{bucket.area}</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {bucket.items.map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-muted">
                  <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0">→</span>{item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- The investor standard -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto card border-teal-DEFAULT/30 bg-teal-glow p-8 text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <p class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT text-lg font-semibold mb-3">
          What we are looking for in a capital partner.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-left mb-6">
          {[
            'Alignment with the liberation-grounded vision — not just the financials',
            'Understanding that justice-centered frameworks are the future of organizational health',
            'Patient capital that supports a build designed for scale, not a quick exit',
            'Connections and relationships in the enterprise, nonprofit, and academic markets',
            'Respect for the founder\'s intellectual authority and methodological sovereignty',
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-muted">
              <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0">✓</span>{item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted text-xs italic">
          Strategic Transformations is not looking for investors who want to change the vision.
          We are looking for investors who understand what it is — and want to build it with us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── CTA ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-16 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-light mb-4">
        Ready to explore alignment?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm">
        All investor conversations begin with an Executive Briefing.
        The full investor deck — including financial projections, revenue model detail,
        and capitalization structure — is available by request only after vetting.
      </p>
      <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-teal text-base !py-4 !px-8">
        Request Investor Briefing →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
